  "description": "Code and resources showcasing the Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) technique, a solution for enhancing data freshness in Large Language Models (LLMs). Incorporate up-to-date external knowledge into LLM-generated responses. Additionally, this repository includes a Gradio-based user interface for seamless model deployment. ",
